{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Protocol/H1.html#Std.Http.Protocol.H1.Machine.pullBody\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">Protocol</span>.<span class=\"name\">H1</span>.<span class=\"name\">Machine</span>.<span class=\"name\">pullBody</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">dir</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Http/Protocol/H1/Message.html#Std.Http.Protocol.H1.Direction\">Direction</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">machine</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Http/Protocol/H1.html#Std.Http.Protocol.H1.Machine\">Machine</a> <span class=\"fn\">dir</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Std/Http/Protocol/H1.html#Std.Http.Protocol.H1.Machine\">Machine</a> <span class=\"fn\">dir</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Std/Http/Protocol/H1.html#Std.Http.Protocol.H1.PulledChunk\">PulledChunk</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Pulls at most one body chunk from the reader.\n\nIt advances body parsing until it either:\n- produces a chunk (`some PulledChunk`), or\n- cannot continue for now (`none`).\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Protocol/H1.html#Std.Http.Protocol.H1.Machine.pullBody","kind":"def","line":1642,"name":"Std.Http.Protocol.H1.Machine.pullBody","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Http/Protocol/H1.lean#L1642-L1663"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Protocol/H1.html#Std.Http.Protocol.H1.Machine.step\"><span c